title: Культові українці. Позначені гривнею
overview: The historical program Культові українці. Позначені гривнею tells about unknown stories about outstanding personalities of Ukraine. The host of the program Yelyzaveta Tsarehradska and the co-host, historian Oleksandr Alforov will tell little-known facts from the biographies of the figures depicted on the hryvnia banknotes without complicated terms.
